<html>
  <head>
    <title></title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Anton+SC&family=Open+Sans:ital,wght@0,300..800;1,300..800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/shared.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/index.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="layout__wrapper">
      <header class="layout__container">
        <img src="/img/header-background.jpg" width="960" alt="" />
        <img src="/img/astero.png" width="350" id="astero-one" alt="" />
        <img src="/img/astero.png" width="180" id="astero-two" alt="" />
        <nav>
          <a href=""><img src="/img/logo-regular.jpg" width="90" alt="" /></a>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="">Delete</a></li>
          </ul>
        </nav>
      </header>
      <main class="layout__container">
        <div class="">
          <h1>EVE-Online Account Verification</h1>
          <p>To access our Discord you must link your EVE-Online account. We're mostly interested in your current account status and active corporation, we use this data to assign roles and set what you can and cannot see in Discord.</p>
          {{#if hash}}
            <p><span class="presentation__notice-bar presentation__notice-bar--info"><img src="/img/icons/notice-outline.svg" alt="" />You can delete your Sakagami Incorporated account at any time.</span></p>          
            <p class="presentation__text-center"><a href="https://login.eveonline.com/v2/oauth/authorize/?response_type=code&redirect_uri={{redirectUri}}&client_id={{clientID}}&scope=publicData esi-characters.read_corporation_roles.v1 esi-corporations.read_titles.v1&state={{hash}}"><img src="/img/eve-sso-login-black-large.png" alt="Login to EVE-Online" />
            <br /><small class="login-link__wrapper">[ https://login.eveonline.com ]</small></a></p>
          {{else}}
            <p><span class="presentation__notice-bar presentation__notice-bar--error"><img src="/img/icons/notice-outline.svg" alt="" />Discord ID is missing, please start verification from Discord.</span></p>
            <p class="presentation__text-center">Please use the <span class="presentation__inline-code">!verify</span> command in our <span class="presentation__inline-code">#eve-account-link</span> channel in Discord to register, this will capture your Discord ID automatically.</p>
          {{/if}}
        </div>
      </main>
      <footer class="layout__container">
        <p>Website Copyright &copy; 2024-2025 Sakagami Incorporated
        <br />EVE-Online &amp; Associated Materials Copyright Â© CCP 1997-2025</p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>